<li id="cite_note-reuter_usaeu-42"><span class="mw-cite-backlink noprint">↑ <sup><a href="#cite_ref-reuter_usaeu_42-0">a</a> et <a href="#cite_ref-reuter_usaeu_42-1">b</a></sup> </span><span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE5BD4T220091214">U.S., EU urge China to release prominent dissident</a>, <a href="/wiki/Reuters" title="Reuters">Reuters</a>, 14 décembre 2009.</span>
